	   <tr><td colspan=2>With a skill of 180 I made one with 2 tries.&nbsp;&nbsp;I think I got pretty lucky.  I also have the Trueshot bow.  Having used both I prefer the SDCB for both the range and the speed increase.  Match this with affordable 4 damage 150 yard arrows and you have a bow that can reach out and touch someone.  No its not a double recurve velium bow or above.  But the point is that anyone with a few plat can have one of these.  Not everyone ls going to get lucky enough to see let alone touch a Velium bow.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
